---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | AI Agency Mentorship">
  <div class="min-h-screen pt-24 pb-20">
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-20">
      <a href="/" class="text-sm text-accent hover:underline mb-8 inline-block">&larr; Back to Home</a>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm text-secondary mb-8 pb-6 border-b border-slate-200">
        <p><strong>Effective:</strong> January 1, 2025</p>
        <p><strong>Updated:</strong> January 1, 2025</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none text-secondary leading-relaxed">
        <p class="mb-6">Altcutm LLC ("we," "us," or "our") operates AI Agency Mentorship (the "Service"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your personal information when you use our Service.</p>
        <p class="mb-8">By using the Service, you consent to the practices described in this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree, please do not use the Service.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-10 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mt-6 mb-2">a) Personal Information You Provide</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-6">
          <li>Name</li>
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Phone number (optional, for WhatsApp support)</li>
          <li>Payment information (processed securely by Stripe; we do not store full card details)</li>
          <li>Business details (optional)</li>
          <li>Communication data (emails, support messages, course feedback)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mt-6 mb-2">b) Automatically Collected Information</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-6">
          <li>Device information: IP address, browser type, operating system</li>
          <li>Usage data: Pages viewed, time spent, clickstream data</li>
          <li>Cookies and tracking technologies (see Section 8)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mt-6 mb-2">c) Information from Third Parties</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-6">
          <li>Stripe: Payment and transaction data</li>
          <li>Analytics providers: Google Analytics or similar</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-10 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-6">
          <li>Provide the Service: Process subscriptions, deliver content, manage your account</li>
          <li>Communicate: Send course updates, support responses, newsletters</li>
          <li>Process payments: Charge subscription fees, handle refunds (via Stripe)</li>
          <li>Improve the Service: Analyze usage, optimize content, fix bugs</li>
          <li>Marketing: Send promotional emails (you can opt out anytime)</li>
          <li>Legal compliance: Comply with laws, enforce our Terms, prevent fraud</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-10 mb-4">3. Legal Basis for Processing (GDPR)</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-6">
          <li>Contract performance: To provide the Service you subscribed to</li>
          <li>Legitimate interests: To improve the Service and communicate with you</li>
          <li>Consent: For marketing emails (you can withdraw consent anytime)</li>
          <li>Legal obligation: To comply with laws and regulations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-10 mb-4">4. How We Share Your Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We do not sell your personal information. We may share your data with:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-6">
          <li>Service Providers: Stripe (payments), email providers, analytics tools, hosting services</li>
          <li>Legal Requirements: If required by law, court order, or to protect our rights</li>
          <li>Business Transfers: In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-10 mb-4">5. Data Retention</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-6">
          <li>Active accounts: Data retained while your subscription is active</li>
          <li>Canceled accounts: Data retained for up to 12 months after cancellation</li>
          <li>Transaction records: Retained for 7 years (tax and accounting compliance)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-10 mb-4">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-6">
          <li>Access: Request a copy of your personal data</li>
          <li>Correction: Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Deletion: Request deletion of your data (subject to legal obligations)</li>
          <li>Portability: Receive your data in a machine-readable format</li>
          <li>Objection: Object to processing based on legitimate interests</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent: Withdraw consent for marketing emails</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4"><strong class="text-primary">To exercise your rights:</strong> Email <a href="mailto:alt@altcutman.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">alt@altcutman.com</a> or WhatsApp <a href="https://wa.me/64212550493" class="text-accent hover:underline">+64 21 255 0493</a></p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-10 mb-4">7. Security</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-6">
          <li>Encryption (SSL/TLS) for data in transit</li>
          <li>Secure hosting infrastructure</li>
          <li>Access controls and authentication</li>
          <li>Regular security audits</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-6 italic text-sm">No method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-10 mb-4">8. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We use cookies to remember your login, analyze traffic, personalize content, and improve performance.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-4">
          <li>Essential cookies: Required for the Service to function</li>
          <li>Analytics cookies: Help us understand usage (e.g., Google Analytics)</li>
          <li>Marketing cookies: Used for targeted advertising (e.g., Meta Pixel)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-6">You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect functionality.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-10 mb-4">9. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">The Service may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for their privacy practices.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-10 mb-4">10. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">The Service is not intended for children under 18. We do not knowingly collect data from minors.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-10 mb-4">11. International Data Transfers</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">Your data may be transferred to countries other than your own, including New Zealand and the United States. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-10 mb-4">12. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of material changes via email.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-10 mb-4">13. Contact Us</h2>
        <div class="glass-card p-6 mt-4">
          <p class="font-bold text-primary mb-1">Altcutm LLC</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-secondary mb-3">Data Protection Officer: Patrick Altcutman Musson</p>
          <p class="text-sm"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:alt@altcutman.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">alt@altcutman.com</a></p>
          <p class="text-sm"><strong>WhatsApp:</strong> <a href="https://wa.me/64212550493" class="text-accent hover:underline">+64 21 255 0493</a></p>
          <p class="text-sm"><strong>Address:</strong> Mount Maunganui, Tauranga, New Zealand</p>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-secondary/60">By using AI Agency Mentorship, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
